eague, Vigilante 8 and Mario Kart:<br><br>🚗 We took the grit and twisted humour from Twisted Metal.<br>🚀 The customisation options and depth of play from Rocket League.<br>🌇 The personality and tricked out cars of Vigilante 8.<br>💥 And the powerups and accessibility of Mario Kart.",
